responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "5638CFDE4C359AA6D97710A49FB6D5BD", "We hadn\'t been through the Portal but a few hours when we were set upon suddenly. Goblins swarmed all over our whole group. They knocked some of us out, tied us up and put hoods over our heads! Then they dragged us off.")
